"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/9_E6dc8TDSgOXG4rSWcLD.png?height=843&width=843)\\n\\nOrdering and then organising your flag stock is small but important step. Whatever your questions, let‚Äôs resolve them here.\\n\\nThis is part of the ‚Äò**Get Started**‚Äô series in the [EOM](https://mirror.xyz/0xe2A039aB83dB1ea76842FEc23611806d50C4B4Ae/QhvLl3HKyYJ2Z1TVX-rwDjVhwLhwX-QNyRHawRUYZFE)\\n\\nüü° Find a Venue\\nüü† **Order Flags**\\nüü° Assemble a Team\\nüü° Speech\\nüü° First Date\\nüü° Outreach\\nüü° Go, Go, Go!\\nüü° Launch Day\\n\\n## New Here?\\n\\nExact quantities depend on your city, but generally we recommend:\\n\\n* Minimum **100** pages of Home-Country flags\\n* Minimum **80** pages: English dialects including at least 20 UK and 20 US\\n* Minimum **10** pages: French, German, Portuguese and Spanish\\n* Minimum **10** pages: China, Japan, S.Korea, Russia and a light spread of Arabic countries\\n* Generous sprinkling of Latin America especially Argentina, Brazil, Colombia and Mexico\\n* Minimum **1** sheet of Ambassador, Birthday and Sign Language flag\\n* Minimum **1** sheet of each ‚ÄúCommon Design‚Äù (seen in the order page)\\n\\n## Create an Order\\n\\n### Go to the New Order Page\\n\\n1. Log into the Mundo Lingo website with your email and password.\\n2. Select ‚ÄúADMIN‚Äù\\n3. Select ‚ÄúNew Order‚Äù\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/5baIwE0Uph4F228u19K6s.png?height=264&width=706)\\n\\n### Delivery Address / Phone Number\\n\\nUpdate your address and telephone number in your profile before creating an order. When you make an order, these details are used.\\n\\n### Order Review\\n\\nAt the top you will find ‚ÄúOrder Review‚Äù in which the costs of your order are shown. As you enter your order you can hit ‚ÄúCalculate Order‚Äù to get an updated price.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/3K8wYFJRF_2vGSQrnc93j.png?height=295&width=718)\\n\\n### Standard vs Rare Designs\\n\\nUn-check ‚Äò***Rare Designs***‚Äô to see only ‚Äò***Common Designs***‚Äô.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/nPyZsoqrms8Ax8D5NYwG9.png?height=254&width=768)\\n\\n## Customs\\n\\nEach country has its own import rules. While most countries receive our deliveries with no extra costs there are a few that charge extra. Mundo Lingo is not responsible for any charges incurred by your countries‚Äô customs officials.\\n\\n## Estimated Time of Arrival\\n\\nOur suppliers work hard to get deliveries to you as fast as possible. The official ETA for orders is 14 days. Managers should not expect orders to arrive before this. Our suppliers may accept ‚ÄúUrgent‚Äù requests for Managers who order late, but only up to 10 days ETA. It‚Äôs not possible to make orders arrive in less than 10 days, please don‚Äôt ask (or pressure) suppliers to do so.\\n\\n## Strikes\\n\\n**Minimum Stock**\\n\\nManagers are required to hold a minimum stock at all times. Managers holding less than minimum stock are obligated to make a new order, else face a [strike](https://mirror.xyz/0xe2A039aB83dB1ea76842FEc23611806d50C4B4Ae/4brsyN2C8nGxW-8a8BTfpgOMpBKwr_Fp3MSPXBmtrKo).\\n\\n* Promo Cards | **500**\\n* Posters | **20**\\n* Home Country Flags | **25 pages**\\n* English Speaking (Combined) | **25**\\n* Chinese, French, German, Italian, Japanese, Portuguese, Russian, Spanish | **5 of each**\\n\\n### Penalties for the Under-stocked\\n\\nIf reported to be under-stocked, or unable to provide proof of holding minimum stock on request, Managers are given notice from which 7 days grace is given to make an order. After this period the Managers receive a [strike](https://mirror.xyz/0xe2A039aB83dB1ea76842FEc23611806d50C4B4Ae/4brsyN2C8nGxW-8a8BTfpgOMpBKwr_Fp3MSPXBmtrKo) or penalty. Another 7 days may result in a suspension of licence to run Mundo Lingo events.\\n\\n### Local Printing\\n\\nStock must come from Mundo Lingo-designated suppliers. CM‚Äôs who print locally or use stock not provided by ML, will receive a [strike](https://mirror.xyz/0xe2A039aB83dB1ea76842FEc23611806d50C4B4Ae/4brsyN2C8nGxW-8a8BTfpgOMpBKwr_Fp3MSPXBmtrKo) and penalty.\\n\\n## Now what?\\n\\nNext up, it‚Äôs time to Assemble a Team **\\\\[Link Needed\\\\]**\\n\\n### Go Back\\n\\nüëà [Events Operations Manual](https://mirror.xyz/0xe2A039aB83dB1ea76842FEc23611806d50C4B4Ae/QhvLl3HKyYJ2Z1TVX-rwDjVhwLhwX-QNyRHawRUYZFE)\",\"timestamp\":1639398585,\"title\":\"EOM | Order Flags\"},\"digest\":\"AchnenyXgWri1PSVki4EToc9aXpQV91b3vnWNjNysOI\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xe2A039aB83dB1ea76842FEc23611806d50C4B4Ae\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"34suyCfnLUoFM02SOhmJJJ9iXgiiL5kC6iPH6Fv3LXk\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"jtVAiplEVAd0RPMj7L2P0umm9wTPdvk-kh1vAJTvwJc\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"BW0PjJ7xaFL1kX9WCgDCo_1G_ZJM7qsm1OfXMYrwOs4yfZQPe5mhJp8mzx4E5n1L7j-dBzlDqW8ICaodLobjGA\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x57d0f7cbea22222afabed23e09ac819f759269ea4cca2a83cdd992ddf3ffe88d22a7afd325b70c3c1ae7dee6f5fc8e22188ba69c589cf1f0528e258261121ae51b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"34suyCfnLUoFM02SOhmJJJ9iXgiiL5kC6iPH6Fv3LXk\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"jtVAiplEVAd0RPMj7L2P0umm9wTPdvk-kh1vAJTvwJc\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"xTansKsBjo462mukYF2qo8W0jJ7auH4hB9Of9aiGpBk\"}"